&lt;h2&gt;What people say about the newsletter.&lt;/h2&gt;
  
  &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot; lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Subscribe to &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sfioritto&quot;&gt;@sfioritto&lt;/a&gt; &amp;#39;s newsletter, sometimes you get gems like this: &lt;a href=&quot;http://t.co/nZEjW3GKcx&quot;&gt;http://t.co/nZEjW3GKcx&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Well said, Sir.&lt;/p&gt;&amp;mdash; Travis Neilson (@travisneilson) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/travisneilson/statuses/420675470649085953&quot;&gt;January 7, 2014&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
  
  &lt;blockquote&gt;&quot;Thanks for these Sean. Your e-mails continue to be both insightful and inspiring.&quot;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
  
  &lt;blockquote&gt;&quot;I just wanted to tell you this is one of the best newsletters I&apos;ve gotten in the past year. &quot;&lt;/blockquote&gt;
  
  
  &lt;h3&gt;Who am I?&lt;/h3&gt;
  
  &lt;figure class=&quot;me&quot;&gt;
    &lt;img src=&quot;/images/me.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Sean Fioritto&quot;&gt;&lt;/img&gt;
  &lt;/figure&gt;
  
  &lt;p&gt;
    Hey there, I&apos;m Sean, and I&apos;m probably a lot like you. I make stuff for the web. My web dev skills are mostly self-taught over the last decade or so and I really love what I do.
  &lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;
    Recently, I wrote a book on web development called &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sketchingwithcss.com/&quot;&gt;Sketching with CSS&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;m also an &lt;a href=&quot;http://coding.smashingmagazine.com/2013/11/18/the-future-of-video-in-web-design/&quot;&gt;author in Smashing Magazine&lt;/a&gt; and I&apos;ve written some &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/sfioritto/charlie.js&quot;&gt;cool open source projects&lt;/a&gt;.
  &lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;
    Today, I&apos;m an entrepreneur. In the not so distant past I did the usual 9-5 thing doing web development for a couple big companies.
  &lt;/p&gt;
  
  &lt;p&gt;
    I&apos;d love to meet you on Twitter. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/sfioritto&quot; class=&quot;twitter-follow-button&quot; data-show-count=&quot;true&quot; &gt;Follow @sfioritto&lt;/a&gt;

  &lt;/p&gt;
  
